---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 目录
description: 文章归档
---

<section class="intro">
  <p>这里记录我在学习与项目中的关键节点与思考。</p>
</section>

{% for group in collections.postsByYear %}
  <section class="year-block">
    <h2 class="year">{{ group.year }}</h2>
    <div class="card-grid">
      {% for post in group.posts %}
        <article class="card">
          <a class="card-link" href="{{ post.url }}">
            <div class="card-meta">
              <time datetime="{{ post.date | dateISO }}">{{ post.date | dateISO }}</time>
              {% if post.data.category %}
                <span class="card-chip">{{ post.data.category }}</span>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            <h3 class="card-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
            {% if post.data.description %}
              <p class="card-desc">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
            {% endif %}
          </a>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
{% endfor %}
